76px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Ghana’s Vice President Mahamudu Bawumia has conceded defeat a day after a tense presidential election, marking a historic political comeback for the opposition candidate, former leader John Mahama.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit000w3b6mcbsgyxdu@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Bawumia said in his concession speech on Sunday morning that internally collated results showed that “Mahama has won the presidential election decisively,” ahead of a formal announcement by the electoral commission.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit000x3b6mqf0sx67v@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Bawumia said the opposition National Democratic Congress (NDC) party had also won the parliamentary election. He said he conceded “to avoid further tension and preserve the peace of our country.”</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/sharethrough@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:5},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:3}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot/instances/cnn-v1@published\" class=\"ad-slot\" data-path=\"end/ad-slot-dynamic[0]/items\" data-desktop-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-mobile-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: center; width: 852.667px; height: auto; display: flex; min-height: 0px; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; visibility: hidden; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0px 4px; max-width: 350px; margin-right: auto; width: 350px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: auto; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); user-select: none;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__ad-label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: block; cursor: default; margin-top: 4px;\"></div><div data-ad-type=\"DISPLAY\" data-ad-identifier=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" class=\"ad-feedback-link\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 4px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; color: rgb(110, 110, 110);\"><div class=\"ad-feedback-link__label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit000y3b6m6c10q14h@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">“I have since called H.E John Dramani Mahama to congratulate him as President-elect of the Republic of Ghana,” Bawumia said, adding that “the people have voted for change at this time, and we respect that decision with all humility.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit000z3b6mgdq8762s@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Opinion polls had predicted a first-round victory for Mahama amid widespread discontent over the country’s economy and<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></strong>a crisis over<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/interactive/asequals/ghana-illegal-gold-mining-galamsey-birth-defects-as-equals-intl-cmd/\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">illegal gold mining</a>.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4flik6i00083b6mvguqz8dm@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Ghanaians have been railing against environmental degradation caused by unlicensed small-scale mining, a longstanding issue that has left large swathes of land pockmarked by pits and major rivers polluted.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/outstream@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:7},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:6}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"ad-slot-dynamic__close\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: block; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; width: 18px; height: 18px; opacity: 0.3; cursor: pointer;\"></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit00103b6mu66a3for@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Ghana is also grappling with its worst economic situation in decades as it reels from high inflation, youth unemployment, and a steep increase in the cost of living.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit00113b6m7fk0sg8b@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Bawumia, 61, a UK-trained economist who chaired the nation’s economic management team, faced criticism ahead of the elections over his handling of the struggling economy. On the campaign trail, Mahama also criticized him for saying little about the economy.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit00123b6mplkp9rdm@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Mahama, 66, described the election as a “defining moment” for Ghana and vowed to “reset” the nation on a path “for good governance and accountability.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4fhvrit00133b6m668193fn@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); font-weight: 400; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">He<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://x.com/JDMahama/status/1865691327394103335\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">said</a><span>&nbsp;</span>Sunday he had received a “congratulatory call” from Bawumia, following his “emphatic victory.”</p></div><div class=\"article__copyright\" data-editable=\"copyright\" itemprop=\"articleCopyright\" data-reorderable=\"copyright\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"></div></div></main></section></article></section>', 11, 1, 1, 1222);
