l.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_653,w_1160,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"605\" width=\"1075\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/still-21166969-40350-529-still.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_605,w_1075,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"833\" width=\"1480\" media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/still-21166969-40350-529-still.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_833,w_1480,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><img src=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/still-21166969-40350-529-still.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_833,w_1480,c_fill\" alt=\"Video geolocated by CNN showed fans scaling a wall as they try to flee from the stadium in Nzérékoré in southeastern Guinea.\" class=\"image__dam-img\" height=\"1080\" width=\"1920\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 852.667px; object-fit: cover; height: 479.99px;\"></div><div class=\"image__metadata\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; margin: 8px auto 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); padding-bottom: 8px;\"><div itemprop=\"caption\" class=\"image__caption attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 4px; order: 2; display: inline;\"><span data-editable=\"metaCaption\" class=\"inline-placeholder\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Video geolocated by CNN showed fans scaling a wall as they try to flee from the stadium in Nzérékoré in southeastern Guinea.</span>&nbsp;</div><figcaption class=\"image__credit\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; text-align: right; order: 1; visibility: visible; padding: 4px 0px; line-height: 20px; display: inline;\">From Social Media</figcaption></div></div></div><div class=\"article__content-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"article__content\" data-editable=\"content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" data-reorderable=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; z-index: 1; margin-right: 0px;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/source/instances/cm46i9tbj006w25p07zvs9c4y@published\" data-component-name=\"source\" class=\"source inline-placeholder\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; float: left; z-index: 1; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><cite class=\"source__cite\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-style: normal; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); display: flex; flex-direction: row;\"><span class=\"source__location\" data-editable=\"location\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex; margin-right: 0px;\"></span><span class=\"source__text\" data-editable=\"source\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex;\">CNN</span>&nbsp;—&nbsp;</cite></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46i9tbj006x25p01bjoafj2@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">A crowd crush at a soccer match in the west African country of Guinea has left at least 56 people dead and many others injured, authorities said Monday.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46vvd0800013b6m2prrgcgm@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Information minister Fana Soumah said in a statement that investigations were underway into the cause of the crush at a stadium in the southern city of Nzerekore.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46vvq6w00033b6mvcxq42cw@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Social media videos showed fans scrambling to get out of the packed stadium.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/sharethrough@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:5},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:3}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot/instances/cnn-v1@published\" class=\"ad-slot\" data-path=\"end/ad-slot-dynamic[0]/items\" data-desktop-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-mobile-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: center; width: 852.667px; height: auto; display: flex; min-height: 0px; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; visibility: hidden; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0px 4px; max-width: 350px; margin-right: auto; width: 350px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: auto; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); user-select: none;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__ad-label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; cursor: default; margin-top: 4px;\"></div><div data-ad-type=\"DISPLAY\" data-ad-identifier=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" class=\"ad-feedback-link\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 4px; cursor: pointer; display: flex;\"><div class=\"ad-feedback-link__label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i00073b6mv5gfhhdn@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">“The government deplores the incidents that marred the football match between the Labé and Nzérékoré teams this afternoon in Nzérékoré,” Prime Minister Bah Oury said earlier in a statement.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i00093b6m8sjtsu1b@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">“The government is monitoring the development of the situation and reiterates its call for calm so that hospital services are not hindered in providing first aid to the injured,” Oury said, with city authorities ordered to restore “social tranquality.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000a3b6muzy5b5rx@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Oury’s statement did not give an account of what happened inside the stadium, but he said a more detailed report would follow.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000b3b6mhj94z938@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Video geolocated by CNN showed fans scaling a wall as they tried to flee the stadium in Nzérékoré in southeastern Guinea.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000e3b6m6dkyhmx3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Mediaguinee said clashes between fans and security began over a series of refereeing decisions followed by a stampede as crowds tried to escape the stadium.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000f3b6m8cm6b7tv@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">CNN has not been able to verify those reports.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46vsrii00003b6m99whazyg@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Witnesses told Reuters that the chaos started after the referee officiating the game sent off a player in the dying minutes, sparking outrage and stone-pelting from angry fans.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm472cicl000a3b6m2alj8vd5@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">“The stone-throwing started and the police joined in, firing tear gas. In the rush and scramble that followed, I saw people fall to the ground, girls and children trampled underfoot. It was horrible,” Amara Conde, who was at the stadium, told the news agency.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4722wik00083b6m64j3b3ev@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Deposed former leader Alpha Conde criticized organizers for holding the match at a time when “the country is already marked by tensions and restrictions.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm472l529000f3b6mkdz23h3m@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Conde, who was ousted by junta leader Mamady Doumbouya in a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2021/09/05/africa/guinea-coup-intl/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">2021 coup</a>, added that “while severe restrictions are maintained on events and rallies, including sports-related ones, it is imperative that we examine how this event was planned and executed.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000g3b6mwhj49r6v@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Local media outlet&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.avenirguinee.org/urgent-declaration-du-fndc-sur-le-drame-a-nzerekore/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Avenirguinee</a>&nbsp;reported that the match was part of a tournament organized by Guinea’s ruling military junta to support Doumbouya’s candidacy.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000h3b6mvctevzfb@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">After seizing power, Doumbouya&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2021/10/01/africa/guinea-coup-leader-sworn-president-intl/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">installed himself as president,</a>&nbsp;and is eyeing a potential presidential run in elections expected to be held in 2025.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000i3b6mgkd3sf8i@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Doumbouya is one of several figures who have seized power in the volatile region since 2020.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm46icl5i000j3b6mxaawicnt@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">West and Central Africa have seen at least eight successful coups since 2020, as political upheavals exacerbate concerns of a slide towards military rule in a resource-rich but poverty-stricken region.</p></div></div>', 11, 0, 1, 4564);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (3, 3, 'https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/456_285/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/z61149450792530704d4d3091988ec3fb20658733ca71c-17337959000931164362877.jpg', 'Chinese fishing vessel under control of suspected pirates off Somali coast, EU naval force says', '2024-12-23', 'The climate crisis and its global impact.', '<p><br></p><div class=\"image__lede article__lede-wrapper\" data-editable=\"lede\" data-freewheel-lede=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/image/instances/cm4cgvxv7000t3b6mv2s8gjgt@published\" class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small image--eq-small\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"PLAnavy_reuters.jpg\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.5626666666666666\" data-original-height=\"1688\" data-original-width=\"3000\" data-url=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/planavy-reuters.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding-bottom: 0px; width: 852.667px;\"><div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 525}\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; margin-bottom: auto;\"><source height=\"653\" width=\"1160\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/planavy-reuters.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_653,w_1160,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"605\" width=\"1075\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/planavy-reuters.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_605,w_1075,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"833\" width=\"1480\" media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/planavy-reuters.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_833,w_1480,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><img src=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/planavy-reuters.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_833,w_1480,c_fill\" alt=\"A Chinese People\'s Liberation Army Navy vessel transits the Gulf of Aden prior to conducting a bilateral counter-piracy exercise with the U.S. Navy in 2012.\" class=\"image__dam-img\" height=\"1688\" width=\"3000\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 852.667px; object-fit: cover; height: 479.99px;\"></div><div class=\"image__metadata\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; margin: 8px auto 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); padding-bottom: 8px;\"><div itemprop=\"caption\" class=\"image__caption attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 4px; order: 2; display: inline;\"><span data-editable=\"metaCaption\" class=\"inline-placeholder\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">A Chinese People\'s Liberation Army Navy vessel transits the Gulf of Aden prior to conducting a bilateral counter-piracy exercise with the U.S. Navy in 2012.</span>&nbsp;</div><figcaption class=\"image__credit\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; text-align: right; order: 1; visibility: visible; padding: 4px 0px; line-height: 20px; display: inline;\">Mass Communication Specialist 2nd Class Aaron Chase/U.S. Navy/Reuters/File</figcaption></div></div></div><div class=\"article__content-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"article__content\" data-editable=\"content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" data-reorderable=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; z-index: 1; margin-right: 0px;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/source/instances/cm4cfysdr002f2bqcdcdn63q8@published\" data-component-name=\"source\" class=\"source inline-placeholder\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; float: left; z-index: 1; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><cite class=\"source__cite\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-style: normal; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); display: flex; flex-direction: row;\"><span class=\"source__location\" data-editable=\"location\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex; margin-right: 6px;\">Hong Kong</span><span class=\"source__text\" data-editable=\"source\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex;\">CNN</span>&nbsp;—&nbsp;</cite></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfysdr002g2bqcc8bwgelh@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/world/china\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Chinese</a>&nbsp;fishing vessel off the coast of Somalia has come under the control of alleged pirates, a European Union anti-piracy force operating in the area said Thursday.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai700063b6mkeeszemz@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The ship, with up to 18 crew members, had been taken over by the suspected pirates, some of whom were armed with AK-47s and machine guns, the European Union Naval Force Operation Atalanta said in a statement.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai700073b6mm25hicld@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">It classified the incident as a robbery at sea and said none of the crew had been injured.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/sharethrough@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:5},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:3}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot/instances/cnn-v1@published\" class=\"ad-slot\" data-path=\"end/ad-slot-dynamic[0]/items\" data-desktop-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-mobile-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: center; width: 852.667px; height: auto; display: flex; min-height: 0px; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; visibility: hidden; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0px 4px; max-width: 350px; margin-right: auto; width: 350px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: auto; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); user-select: none;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__ad-label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; cursor: default; margin-top: 4px;\"></div><div data-ad-type=\"DISPLAY\" data-ad-identifier=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" class=\"ad-feedback-link\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 4px; cursor: pointer; display: flex;\"><div class=\"ad-feedback-link__label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai700083b6mcyvmfscx@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The force had responded to an alert from police in Somalia’s semi-autonomous northeastern Puntland region that a Chinese ship off the coast had allegedly been hijacked, its statement said.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai700093b6myi5ynv02@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">China has yet to comment on the situation, which occurred in a key region for its overseas naval activities guarding the country’s expanded footprint and economic interests in Africa and the Middle East.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000a3b6m8x9p2obk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The People’s Liberation Army Navy has since 2008 conducted anti-piracy operations around the Gulf of Aden along Somalia’s northern coast as one of a number of major powers seeking to secure shipping routes in the face of rampant piracy.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/outstream@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:7},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:6}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"ad-slot-dynamic__close\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; width: 18px; height: 18px; opacity: 0.3; cursor: pointer;\"></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000b3b6mzj6nlftj@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">And since 2017 China has operated its only overseas military base in Djibouti, also on the Horn of Africa.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000c3b6m3wbjvj9v@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The latest incident comes amid a recent uptick in piracy in the area, which is close to key international shipping lanes through the Suez Canal and Red Sea.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000d3b6mvchi8xic@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The slow resurgence follows&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2023/12/19/politics/houthi-red-sea-attacks/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">attacks by Houthi rebels on commercial shipping</a>&nbsp;in the Red Sea in retaliation for Israel’s war on Hamas in Gaza. The attacks, which began late last year and decreased in the spring, upended global trade – and diluted the attention of international naval forces in the region, observers say.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000e3b6mtvdza619@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The EU’s Operation Atalanta recorded 19 attacks by suspected pirates so far this year – the highest number since 2012, according to data from the force, which operates in waters around the Horn of Africa and the Western Indian Ocean.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000f3b6m4oh69605@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">That’s still a far cry from the peak of 2011 when there were 212 attacks, the data shows.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000g3b6mcm19zatp@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The earlier decline is widely attributed to coordinated and UN-backed international efforts, including from NATO, the EU and UN Security Council permanent members, which gained steam from 2008.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000h3b6mhgt4i1b6@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The Chinese navy’s now-longstanding anti-piracy task force began conducting escort missions in the Gulf of Aden and the waters off Somalia in December 2008 after a spate of attacks on Chinese vessels.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000i3b6mo8968tyx@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">At the time, the start of that taskforce marked a step forward in China’s efforts to use its growing international clout and economic strength to address shared international issues.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000j3b6mrqif73xk@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">China’s navy has since run more than 40 escort missions of international and Chinese vessels in the region, but did not join a US-led multinational coalition to protect ships transiting the Red Sea against the Houthi attacks.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4cfzai7000k3b6mcwvdftsb@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The EU’s Operation Atalanta said it was in “permanent contact” with Somali and Chinese authorities on the latest incident. CNN has reached out to China’s Foreign Ministry and Ministry of Defense for comment.</p></div></div>', 12, 1, 1, 1234);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (4, 4, 'https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/456_285/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/z61149450792530704d4d3091988ec3fb20658733ca71c-17337959000931164362877.jpg', 'China is probing Nvidia in a major escalation of its chip war with the US', '2024-12-24', 'A journey into the stars.', '<p><br></p><div class=\"image__lede article__lede-wrapper\" data-editable=\"lede\" data-freewheel-lede=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/image/instances/cm4gzxhrt006925p5a2yv5ock@published\" class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small image--eq-small\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"GettyImages-1988609819.jpg\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.6846666666666666\" data-original-height=\"2054\" data-original-width=\"3000\" data-url=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1988609819.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding-bottom: 0px; width: 852.667px;\"><div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 525}\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; margin-bottom: auto;\"><source height=\"605\" width=\"1075\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1988609819.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"653\" width=\"1160\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1988609819.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><img src=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1988609819.jpg?c=16x9\" alt=\"Nvidia headquarters in Santa Clara, California.\" class=\"image__dam-img\" height=\"2054\" width=\"3000\" pinger-seen=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 852.667px; object-fit: cover; height: 479.479px;\"></div><div class=\"image__metadata\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; margin: 8px auto 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); padding-bottom: 8px;\"><div itemprop=\"caption\" class=\"image__caption attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 4px; order: 2; display: inline;\"><span data-editable=\"metaCaption\" class=\"inline-placeholder\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Nvidia headquarters in Santa Clara, California.</span>&nbsp;</div><figcaption class=\"image__credit\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; text-align: right; order: 1; visibility: visible; padding: 4px 0px; line-height: 20px; display: inline;\">Justin Sullivan/Getty Images</figcaption></div></div></div><div class=\"article__content-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"article__content\" data-editable=\"content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" data-reorderable=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; z-index: 1; margin-right: 0px;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/source/instances/cm4gzxhrs006625p57y7aezun@published\" data-component-name=\"source\" class=\"source inline-placeholder\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; float: left; z-index: 1; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><cite class=\"source__cite\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-style: normal; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); display: flex; flex-direction: row;\"><span class=\"source__location\" data-editable=\"location\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex; margin-right: 0px;\"></span><span class=\"source__text\" data-editable=\"source\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex;\">CNN</span>&nbsp;—&nbsp;</cite></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4gzxhrt006725p5591d5c46@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">China has opened an antitrust investigation into American chipmaker Nvidia, the world’s largest provider of processors that power artificial intelligence, according to Chinese state media.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h03fdv000a356muugtaggf@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The probe serves as the latest escalation of a growing battle for AI dominance, which both the United States and China believe is crucial for national security.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4gzxji10000356moxum4gfv@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><a href=\"https://content-static.cctvnews.cctv.com/snow-book/index.html?item_id=6510218410825795776&amp;t=1733743942733&amp;toc_style_id=feeds_default&amp;track_id=CD2B9262-6EF1-43C2-AE0A-0DB6D3E10C99_755436823622&amp;share_to=copy_url\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">China Central Television</a>&nbsp;in a report Monday said the Chinese government believes Nvidia’s purchase of Israeli networking company Mellanox could violate the country’s anti-monopoly laws, though the report did not specify what the merger did to potentially break the law.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nvidianews.nvidia.com/news/nvidia-receives-approval-to-proceed-with-mellanox-acquisition-from-chinas-antitrust-authority\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">China approved the acquisition</a>&nbsp;in 2020.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h0cja0000o356mipltm75u@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Nvidia (<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/markets/stocks/NVDA\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">NVDA</a>) shares fell less than 2% in premarket trading Monday. The stock is among the hottest on the market, surging nearly 200% this year as the AI boom has fueled demand for the company’s chips. Its market value is more than $3 trillion, second only to Apple.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h0pahf000u356mqerf9ph3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The tit-for-tat China-US chip war has entered a new phase this month, after the Biden administration imposed another round of restrictions on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2024/12/08/tech/us-china-hbm-chips-hnk-intl/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">high tech memory chip sales</a>&nbsp;to China a week ago. The memory chips are different than the graphics processors Nvidia makes, but they are also crucial technology that helps power AI.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h0zwjc000x356mbzoyuxk8@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The administration’s new export controls are the third such round of chip sales restrictions to China. The United States fears that China could use AI to gain a military advantage, and US Commerce Department officials said they believed the restrictions would slow China’s development of AI chips — and industry experts believe the US government’s plan will work.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/outstream@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:7},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:6}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"ad-slot-dynamic__close\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; width: 18px; height: 18px; opacity: 0.3; cursor: pointer;\"></div><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot/instances/cnn-v1@published\" class=\"ad-slot\" data-path=\"end/ad-slot-dynamic[2]/items\" data-desktop-slot-id=\"ad_out_vid_01\" data-mobile-slot-id=\"ad_out_vid_01\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: center; width: 852.667px; height: auto; display: flex; min-height: 0px; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; visibility: hidden; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0px 4px; max-width: 350px; margin-right: auto; width: 350px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: auto; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); user-select: none;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__ad-label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; cursor: default; margin-top: 4px;\"></div><div data-ad-type=\"DISPLAY\" data-ad-identifier=\"ad_out_vid_01\" class=\"ad-feedback-link\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 4px; cursor: pointer; display: flex;\"><div class=\"ad-feedback-link__label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h172l90012356ma80c97b3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">But China’s Commerce Ministry lambasted the United States’ restrictions, saying they pose “a significant threat” to the stability of global supply chains. China’s government&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2024/12/02/tech/china-us-chips-new-restrictions-intl-hnk/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">retaliated last week</a>&nbsp;by banning the sale of materials essential for manufacturing the chips, including germanium and gallium.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h1phpc0018356mg3jaav74@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">A year ago, China had curbed the sale of those materials but created loopholes that allowed for some sales to continue. Those have now been closed.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h23kkn001b356mspn6jcfs@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Senior US officials have also accused China of stealing American-made AI software, which Beijing denies.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h172l90013356m7sux1p6p@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The Nvidia investigation ups the ante. The company is the face of the AI tech revolution and hurting Nvidia could harm the American company’s ambitions to continue to power AI around the world.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h16ah30010356msg4tov7e@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Nvidia is also under antitrust scrutiny in the United States, according to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-gets-doj-subpoena-in-escalating-antitrust-investigation\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Bloomberg</a>.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h25ctb001e356mqabxfnty@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">In addition to curbing materials and chips sales, both China and the United States are trying to bolster their own development and manufacturing of microprocessors at home.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4h27x3q001j356m9ze2rngu@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Through the CHIPS Act, the Biden administration has pumped billions of dollars into Intel and other companies to boost domestic production of chips and reduce America’s reliance on China and other foreign countries for the technology. Meanwhile, China in May announced plans to set up its largest-ever semiconductor state investment fund&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2024/05/27/tech/china-semiconductor-investment-fund-intl-hnk/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">worth $47.5 billion</a>, funded by investments from six of the country’s largest state-owned banks.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4gzxhrt006825p5gpsbfixq@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">This story has been updated with additional developments and context.</em></p></div></div>', 13, 0, 1, 9741);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (5, 5, 'https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/456_285/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/z61149450792530704d4d3091988ec3fb20658733ca71c-17337959000931164362877.jpg', 'Considering moving out of the US in 2025? These are the best countries for American expats', '2024-12-09', 'Key health trends shaping the future.', '<p><br></p><div class=\"image__lede article__lede-wrapper\" data-editable=\"lede\" data-freewheel-lede=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: medium; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/image/instances/cm4d12jh5000a3b6m1uo5ztos@published\" class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small image--eq-small\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"GettyImages-1326910770.jpg\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.6664864864864865\" data-original-height=\"1233\" data-original-width=\"1850\" data-url=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1326910770.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding-bottom: 0px; width: 852.667px;\"><div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 525}\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; margin-bottom: auto;\"><source height=\"653\" width=\"1160\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1326910770.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_653,w_1160,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"605\" width=\"1075\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1326910770.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_605,w_1075,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"833\" width=\"1480\" media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1326910770.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_833,w_1480,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><img src=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-1326910770.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_833,w_1480,c_fill\" alt=\"Italy is a popular destination for people hoping to move abroad. This is a scenic view of Positano on the Amalfi Coast. But would this spot make a good home?\" class=\"image__dam-img\" height=\"1233\" width=\"1850\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 852.667px; object-fit: cover; height: 479.99px;\"></div><div class=\"image__metadata\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; margin: 8px auto 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); padding-bottom: 8px;\"><div itemprop=\"caption\" class=\"image__caption attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 4px; order: 2; display: inline;\"><span data-editable=\"metaCaption\" class=\"inline-placeholder\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Italy is a popular destination for people hoping to move abroad. This is a scenic view of Positano on the Amalfi Coast. But would this spot make a good home?</span>&nbsp;</div><figcaption class=\"image__credit\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; text-align: right; order: 1; visibility: visible; padding: 4px 0px; line-height: 20px;\">Antonel/iStockphoto/Getty Images</figcaption></div></div></div><div class=\"article__content-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: medium; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: cnn_sans_display, helveticaneue, Helvetica, Arial, Utkal, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"article__content\" data-editable=\"content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" data-reorderable=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; z-index: 1; margin-right: 0px;\"><p data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/editor-note/instances/cm4d1d6uy000l3b6mw05qj1ep@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"editor-note\" class=\"editor-note vossi-editor-note inline-placeholder \" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); color: var(--appr-color-text-tertiary); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Editor’s note: Sign up for&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/newsletters/travel?source=nl-acq_article\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--appr-color-text-link-secondary-default); text-decoration-line: var(--base-font-text-decoration-underline); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--base-space-04);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Unlocking the World, CNN Travel’s weekly newsletter</em></a><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">. Get news about destinations, plus the latest in aviation, food and drink, and where to stay.</em></p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/source/instances/cm4d0y1bs002j26pb0jn28osv@published\" data-component-name=\"source\" class=\"source inline-placeholder\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; float: left; z-index: 1; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><cite class=\"source__cite\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-style: normal; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height--from-small); display: flex; flex-direction: row;\"><span class=\"source__location\" data-editable=\"location\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex; margin-right: 0px;\"></span><span class=\"source__text\" data-editable=\"source\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: inline-flex;\">CNN</span>&nbsp;—&nbsp;</cite></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d0y1bs002k26pbgh02gbhq@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Since the US presidential election, there’s been a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cnn.com/travel/americans-moving-abroad-after-election/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">spike</a>&nbsp;in Americans’ interest in moving abroad.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00013b6mf499kdez@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">“It’s been such a gut reaction of, ‘I want to move, but I don’t know where, and I don’t know how,’ ” says Arielle Tucker, a&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.connectedfinancialplanning.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Switzerland-based certified financial planner</a>&nbsp;who specializes in assisting US citizens in moving abroad and says her business has seen a massive uptick in inquiries.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/sharethrough-travel-style@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--3\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:4},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:2}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot/instances/cnn-v1@published\" class=\"ad-slot\" data-path=\"end/ad-slot-dynamic[0]/items\" data-desktop-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-mobile-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: center; width: 852.667px; height: auto; display: flex; min-height: 0px; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; visibility: hidden; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0px 4px; max-width: 350px; margin-right: auto; width: 350px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: auto; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); user-select: none;\"><div class=\"ad-slot__ad-label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; cursor: default; margin-top: 4px;\"></div><div data-ad-type=\"DISPLAY\" data-ad-identifier=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" class=\"ad-feedback-link\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 4px; cursor: pointer; display: flex;\"><div class=\"ad-feedback-link__label\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00023b6m1qyy8dmy@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Tucker tells CNN Travel, “I think it’s important to always take a step back here and really think about, ‘Well, what countries can I actually move to as an American?’ The harder issue is, if you really want to make that permanent relocation, then you really need to think about, ‘What visa types can I actually get?’ ”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00033b6m6481pdp9@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">According to Google Trends, searches related to phrases such as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/explore?date=all&amp;geo=US&amp;q=leaving%20the%20country&amp;hl=en-GB\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">“leaving the country”</a>&nbsp;and “how to move to Canada” skyrocketed in November 2024, following the news that Donald Trump would be returning to the White House. It’s been even more than the exponential rise in similar searches after he won the 2016 election. (Back then,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/11/09/501352852/canadas-immigration-website-has-been-down-for-hours\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Canada’s immigration website crashed</a>.)</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00043b6mprd711rz@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Whether or not a move abroad is politically motivated, the increase of remote work, new visa programs and tax incentives that attract digital nomads, investors, retirees and families have as of late provided additional options for people considering an international move.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00053b6m8lye77me@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Of course, the ability to move abroad is a privilege that extends only to people lucky enough to be in possession of the right passport, with doors remaining closed to many nationalities.</p><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/ad-slot-dynamic/instances/outstream@published\" class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:7},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:6}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; position: relative; justify-content: center; align-items: center; width: 852.667px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"ad-slot-dynamic__close\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; width: 18px; height: 18px; opacity: 0.3; cursor: pointer;\"></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d7bp5n00013b6mwow1vx5e@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Recently, headlines have swirled around the news of several US celebrities moving out of the United States, including Richard Gere, who has publicly discussed his upcoming move to Spain, where his wife is from, and Ellen DeGeneres and her wife, Portia de Rossi, who have reportedly&nbsp;<a href=\"https://people.com/ellen-degeneres-moved-to-england-after-finding-a-house-she-loved-in-the-countryside-source-8749380\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">moved to England’s Cotswolds region</a>.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00063b6m89c7twq1@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-family: var(--theme-paragraph__font-family); font-size: var(--theme-paragraph__font-size); line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">For those who have the option, choosing which country to make your new home is a major decision that requires extensive research and planning. Beyond the “I could live here!” daydreaming that might bubble up during vacation, moving abroad means a deep dive into tax implications, work visas, health care and quality-of-life comparisons, just to name a few.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00073b6mxlx7379k@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">One helpful resource is the annual&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.internations.org/expat-insider/2024/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Expat Insider survey</a>&nbsp;by InterNations, an expat community with more than 5.4 million members. The survey, which has been running for more than a decade, reflects input from more than 12,500 expats representing 175 nationalities in 174 countries or territories. It conveys their satisfaction level with various aspects of expat life on the basis of factors such as quality of life, ease of settling in, working abroad, personal finance, housing and language.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00083b6mxlgk61m3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">In addition, retirees can take advantage of resources including&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.liveandinvestoverseas.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Live and Invest Overseas</a>, whose annual index ranks its top 10 overseas retirement destinations. Its 2024 index saw Valencia, Spain, top the list, followed by Braga, Portugal, and Mazatlán, Mexico.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj00093b6m22gzvt8e@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">It’s also important to consider the impact of your move on a new host country, especially in destinations that are seeing big upticks in immigration from the United States and other wealthy nations, says&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.meganfrye.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Megan Frye</a>, a relocation consultant and writer who has lived in Mexico City for the past nine years.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj000a3b6mvpbesy9x@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Frye advises clients considering a move from the United States to Mexico — which has ranked among the top five countries in InterNations’ annual survey since 2014 — to be aware of the inequities in migration policies between the two countries.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj000b3b6m4e3xuyfi@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">“My focus with my clients is to be very clear about the gentrification problem that Mexico faces, and to give them an opportunity to think about what our role is in that situation,” says Frye, who is originally from Michigan. “I believe all people should be able to move freely wherever they want, but there’s a clear injustice considering how easy it is for US citizens to relocate to Mexico in comparison with the other way around.”</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj000c3b6m0gn6kylb@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">While there are dozens of destinations to consider for a move abroad, the following list prioritizes a range of expat-centric topics, including quality of life, affordability, health care, safety and access to culture and outdoor activities. This list offers general advice for people making the move from anywhere in the world, but focuses primarily on US citizens.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dj000d3b6mharpu0t5@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Also included are some of the downsides to consider, as well as key info on how to make the move.</p><h2 class=\"subheader inline-placeholder\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/subheader/instances/cm4d1r4jc002h3b6mu6gklpe0@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\" id=\"mexico\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: var(--theme-subheader__font-weight); line-height: var(--theme-subheader-h2__line-height); font-size: var(--theme-subheader-h2__font-size); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-subheader__font-family); clear: inherit; padding: 16px 0px 8px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Mexico</h2><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/image/instances/cm4d13frb000g3b6mdjrotzci@published\" class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small image--eq-small\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"GettyImages-647752888.jpg\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.6665\" data-original-height=\"1333\" data-original-width=\"2000\" data-url=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-647752888.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 32px 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; width: 852.667px;\"><div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 525}\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; margin-bottom: auto;\"><picture class=\"image__picture\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 100%; display: contents; height: 0px;\"><source height=\"1333\" width=\"2000\" media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-647752888.jpg?q=w_1110,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"1333\" width=\"2000\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-647752888.jpg?q=w_1015,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"1333\" width=\"2000\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-647752888.jpg?q=w_1160,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"1333\" width=\"2000\" media=\"(max-width: 479px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-647752888.jpg?q=w_680,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><img src=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-647752888.jpg?q=w_1110,c_fill\" alt=\"Mexico regularly ranks highly among countries offering satisfaction for expats. Puerto Vallarta is pictured.\" class=\"image__dam-img\" height=\"1333\" width=\"2000\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 852.667px; object-fit: cover; height: 567.875px;\"></picture></div><div class=\"image__metadata\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; margin: 8px auto 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); padding-bottom: 8px;\"><div itemprop=\"caption\" class=\"image__caption attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 4px; order: 2; display: inline;\"><span data-editable=\"metaCaption\" class=\"inline-placeholder\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Mexico regularly ranks highly among countries offering satisfaction for expats. Puerto Vallarta is pictured.</span>&nbsp;</div><figcaption class=\"image__credit\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; text-align: right; order: 1; visibility: visible; padding: 4px 0px; line-height: 20px;\">ferrantraite/E+/Getty Images</figcaption></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000e3b6mg35m4evs@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">A popular retirement destination for Americans for decades, Mexico has attracted many more families and the digital nomad set over the past few years.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000f3b6m4s40d0en@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Mexico City — whose population of 22 million in the metro area makes it North America’s biggest city — has been especially hot as of late. And the capital’s growth shows no signs of slowing, with about 667,300 more inhabitants projected in 2025 than three years prior, according to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://worldpopulationreview.com/world-cities/mexico-city-population\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">The World Population Review</a>. From<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://portales.segob.gob.mx/es/PoliticaMigratoria/Sintesis_Grafica/?Sintesis=2021\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">2019 to 2022</a>, the number of Americans who applied for or renewed residency visas spiked from about 17,800 to more than 30,000.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000g3b6m3v7lfoo4@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Elsewhere, cities including Oaxaca, San Miguel de Allende and Playa del Carmen are also havens for US expats, many of whom point to Mexico’s lower cost of living and relaxed lifestyle as strong draws.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000h3b6mqop4h16l@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Pros:</span>&nbsp;Mexico topped InterNations’ 2023 Expat Insider survey and has ranked among the top five countries since 2014. According to the latest results, expats appreciate factors such as the ease of settling in, a fulfilling social life and strong support networks. Mexico’s affordability and laid-back lifestyle also score high.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000i3b6migrezckw@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Cons:&nbsp;</span>As with other global destinations that have received an influx of Americans as of late, some Mexican cities with large expat communities are getting pushback against foreigners.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000j3b6mlk60rdzi@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Mexico also has a high crime rate. Homicide rates are nearly four times as those in the United States, according to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/contenidos/saladeprensa/boletines/2022/DH/DH2021.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Mexico’s National Institute of Statistics and Geography</a>. And those numbers may be even higher: Data from the Human Rights Watch suggests that an estimated 90% of crimes in Mexico are never reported.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000k3b6mvv5ro31u@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">How to make the move:</span>&nbsp;Moving to Mexico isn’t as simple as packing a bag, hopping a flight and toasting to your new life south of the border over a margarita on the beach.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000l3b6m0idxa6i4@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Traditionally, valid passport holders from countries that don’t require a visa (including the United States) who are coming to Mexico for leisure or business have been allowed to remain in the country for up to 180 days. (They still must complete a visitor’s permit, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.inm.gob.mx/fmme/publico/en/solicitud.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Forma Migratoria Multiple</a>, FMM for short, at their port of entry.)</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000m3b6mslr9pzyl@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">However, that 180-day limit is no longer the default, and the exact number of days allowed is at the discretion of the immigration official processing entry.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000n3b6mex3rz291@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Mexico does not offer a digital nomad visa, but those considering a permanent move can look into a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://consulmex.sre.gob.mx/leamington/index.php/non-mexicans/visas/115-temporary-resident-visa\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Temporary Resident Visa</a>, which allows you to remain in the country for up to four years. Meanwhile, retirees can apply for a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://consulmex.sre.gob.mx/leamington/index.php/non-mexicans/visas/114-permanent-resident-visa#:~:text=Foreigners%20who%20wish%20to%20remain,to%20their%20place%20of%20residence.&amp;text=Visa%20application%20form%20printed%20on,sided%2C%20properly%20completed%20and%20signed.\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Permanent Resident Visa</a>.</p><h2 class=\"subheader inline-placeholder\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/subheader/instances/cm4d1xq9d003b3b6mb57dc485@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\" id=\"spain\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: var(--theme-subheader__font-weight); line-height: var(--theme-subheader-h2__line-height); font-size: var(--theme-subheader-h2__font-size); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-subheader__font-family); clear: inherit; padding: 16px 0px 8px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Spain</h2><div data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/image/instances/cm4d1xwhm003d3b6mky51e9h4@published\" class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small image--eq-small\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"GettyImages-868272252.jpg\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.6675675675675675\" data-original-height=\"1235\" data-original-width=\"1850\" data-url=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-868272252.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 32px 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; width: 852.667px;\"><div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 525}\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; display: flex; margin-bottom: auto;\"><picture class=\"image__picture\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 100%; display: contents; height: 0px;\"><source height=\"1235\" width=\"1850\" media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-868272252.jpg?q=w_1110,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"1235\" width=\"1850\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-868272252.jpg?q=w_1015,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"1235\" width=\"1850\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-868272252.jpg?q=w_1160,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><source height=\"1235\" width=\"1850\" media=\"(max-width: 479px)\" srcset=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-868272252.jpg?q=w_680,c_fill/f_webp\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><img src=\"https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/gettyimages-868272252.jpg?q=w_1110,c_fill\" alt=\"Spain offers one of the lowest costs of living in Western Europe. And the outdoor cafe scene in Valencia certainly has appeal.\" class=\"image__dam-img\" height=\"1235\" width=\"1850\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; width: 852.667px; object-fit: cover; height: 569.562px;\"></picture></div><div class=\"image__metadata\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; max-width: 676px; margin: 8px auto 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230); padding-bottom: 8px;\"><div itemprop=\"caption\" class=\"image__caption attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 4px; order: 2; display: inline;\"><span data-editable=\"metaCaption\" class=\"inline-placeholder\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Spain offers one of the lowest costs of living in Western Europe. And the outdoor cafe scene in Valencia certainly has appeal.</span>&nbsp;</div><figcaption class=\"image__credit\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; text-align: right; order: 1; visibility: visible; padding: 4px 0px; line-height: 20px;\">RossHelen/iStock Editorial/Getty Images</figcaption></div></div><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000p3b6myrytagya@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">A gorgeous climate, a relatively low cost of living, and vibrant, culture-rich cities and towns from the Mediterranean to the Atlantic: No wonder more Americans are eagerly proclaiming&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">“Viva España!”</em>&nbsp;for their next life chapter.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000q3b6mlfvuwkek@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Madrid, Barcelona, Seville and Bilbao all boast large English-speaking expat communities, while the coastal city of Valencia is quickly gaining traction as a coveted spot, too: It ranked first in InterNations’ 2024&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.internations.org/expat-insider/2024/quality-of-life-index-40451\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Quality of Life Index</a>, and also topped the annual index by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.liveandinvestoverseas.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">Live and Invest Overseas for 2024</a>.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000r3b6m8dzfcqi6@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Pros:&nbsp;</span>There’s&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">mucho</em>&nbsp;to love about Spain: modern cities and quaint small towns, high-quality universal health care and a world-renowned dining and nightlife scene, just to name a few benefits. In fact, the Spanish cities of Valencia, Málaga and Alicante ranked in the top three of InterNations’ most recent list of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.internations.org/expat-insider/2024/best-cities-for-expats-40486\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">best cities for expats</a>.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000s3b6mujk07g7s@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">According to the International LGBTQ+ Travel Association, Spain also is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.iglta.org/destinations/europe/spain/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">one of the most culturally liberal</a>&nbsp;and welcoming countries for LGBTQ+ travelers. In 2005, it became one of the first to legalize same-sex marriage, and it hosts one of the world’s largest Pride celebrations, which draws some 1.5 million visitors every year.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000t3b6mdpl1uig3@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Cons:&nbsp;</span>If you’re hoping moving to Spain will boost your career, you may need to adjust your expectations. According to InterNations’ 2023 survey, “Spain performs worst in the Working Abroad Index (34th). Less than half the expats (49%) agree that moving there has improved their career prospects (vs. 59% globally),” and another 36% are unhappy with the local job market.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000u3b6m1a9cbl20@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">In addition, English is generally not widely spoken outside of larger cities. And, in the regions of Catalonia and the Basque Country, the official languages are Catalan and Euskara (or Basque), respectively.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000v3b6mnoizbszr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">The distinctly Spanish way of life also is an adjustment for many, as schedules for working, dining and socializing are later than American standards. The workday generally runs from 9 a.m. to 7 p.m., with a long lunch break during the afternoon&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">siesta</em>&nbsp;(during which time many businesses are closed), and Spaniards usually eat dinner no earlier than around 8:30 p.m.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000w3b6m8oe35ean@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\">Politics in Spain is also becoming increasingly more divisive (and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2023/11/09/world/spain-vidal-quadras-shot-madrid-intl/index.html\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: var(--theme-paragraph__link-color); text-decoration-line: var(--theme-paragraph__link-decoration); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: var(--base-font-weight-regular); font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); text-underline-offset: var(--theme-paragraph__hover-link-offset);\">occasionally violent</a>), especially as the northeastern region of Catalonia continues its push for independence.</p><p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder vossi-paragraph\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com/_components/paragraph/instances/cm4d1r3dk000x3b6m634a3w7j@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-article-gutter=\"true\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--base-space-16); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); flex: 1 0 0px; line-height: var(--theme-paragraph__line-height); overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 676px; position: relative; left: calc(-543px + 50vw);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: var(--theme-font-family-body); font-size: var(--appr-font-size-body-md); line-height: var(--appr-font-line-height-body-md); color: var(--appr-color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--base-font-letter-spacing-none); flex: 1 0 0px; font-weight: 700;\">How to make the move:&nbsp;</span>Several options exist for expats, including retirees', 14, 1, 1, 205);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (6, 6, 'https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/zoom/456_285/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/z61149450792530704d4d3091988ec3fb20658733ca71c-17337959000931164362877.jpg', 'TP.HCM trình đề án táo bạo: Nâng gấp đôi quy mô metro, làm 355km trong 10 năm', '2024-12-10', 'Renewable energy technologies are evolving rapidly.', '<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto;\">Quốc hội Hàn Quốc vừa thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu nhanh chóng bắt giữ 8 nhân vật chủ chốt, trong đó có Tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol.</h2><div data-check-position=\"body_start\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14px;\"></div><div class=\"detail-cmain clearfix\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px; clear: both; padding-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); max-width: 100%;\"><figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; display: inline-block; flex-direction: column; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: auto; position: relative; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; width: 660px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word; cursor: default; max-width: 100%;\"><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/quoc-hoi-han-quoc-17338137417301874191829.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"content\" data-caption=\"Phiên họp của Quốc hội Hàn Quốc ngày 10-12 đã thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu nhanh chóng bắt giữ 8 nhân vật chủ chốt, trong đó có tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol - Ảnh: Yonhap News\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; color: rgb(34, 106, 197); outline: 0px !important;\"><img data-author=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/730/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/quoc-hoi-han-quoc-17338137417301874191829.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 800px, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/480/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/quoc-hoi-han-quoc-17338137417301874191829.jpg  480w,https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/800/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/quoc-hoi-han-quoc-17338137417301874191829.jpg 800w,https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/1200/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/quoc-hoi-han-quoc-17338137417301874191829.jpg 1200w\" id=\"img_790834943171743744\" w=\"1200\" h=\"689\" alt=\"Quốc hội Hàn Quốc thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu bắt Tổng thống Yoon - Ảnh 1.\" title=\"\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"790834943171743744\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/quoc-hoi-han-quoc-17338137417301874191829.jpg\" type=\"photo\" width=\"1200\" height=\"689\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"lightbox-content\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; width: 660px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast; color: transparent; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; vertical-align: top;\"></a><div id=\"wrapper-inimage-pos-sponsor-0\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><div id=\"in-images\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><div id=\"zone-joqxux31\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><div id=\"share-joqxuxkg\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); padding: 8px 0px;\"><p data-placeholder=\"Nhập chú thích ảnh\" class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(143, 143, 143); margin-bottom: 0px !important; font-size: 16px !important;\">Phiên họp của Quốc hội Hàn Quốc ngày 10-12 đã thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu nhanh chóng bắt giữ 8 nhân vật chủ chốt, trong đó có tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol - Ảnh: Yonhap News</p></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Theo Hãng tin Yonhap, ngày 10-12, Quốc hội Hàn Quốc đã thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu bắt giữ khẩn cấp 8 nhân vật chủ chốt, bao gồm Tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol, liên quan đến việc&nbsp;<a class=\"link-inline-content\" href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/tong-thong-han-quoc-ban-bo-lenh-thiet-quan-luat-khan-cap-20241203214055815.htm\" title=\"ban bố thiết quân luật khẩn cấp\" data-rel=\"follow\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; color: rgb(34, 106, 197); outline: 0px;\">ban bố thiết quân luật khẩn cấp</a>&nbsp;hồi tuần trước.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Nghị quyết được thông qua với 191 phiếu thuận, 94 phiếu chống và 3 phiếu trắng trên tổng số 288 đại biểu tham gia bỏ phiếu.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Nghị quyết yêu cầu bắt giữ khẩn cấp Tổng thống Yoon, cựu Bộ trưởng Quốc phòng&nbsp;<a class=\"link-inline-content\" href=\"https://tuoitre.vn/han-quoc-bat-cuu-bo-truong-quoc-phong-tham-gia-lap-thiet-quan-luat-20241208073822528.htm\" title=\"Kim Yong Hyun\" data-rel=\"follow\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; color: rgb(34, 106, 197); outline: 0px;\">Kim Yong Hyun</a>, cựu Bộ trưởng Nội vụ và An toàn Lee Sang Min.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Ngoài ra, các nhân vật khác bị yêu cầu bắt giữ bao gồm Đại tướng Park An So, Tổng Tham mưu trưởng Lục quân và từng là Chỉ huy trưởng thiết quân luật; Trung tướng Yeo In Hyung, lãnh đạo Phản gián; Trung tướng Lee Jin Woo, lãnh đạo Bộ tư lệnh Phòng thủ thủ đô; Trung tướng Kwak Jong Keun, lãnh đạo Bộ tư lệnh Đặc nhiệm lục quân; Tư lệnh Cảnh sát Quốc gia Hàn Quốc Cho Ji Ho.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Nghị quyết này trước đó đã được Ủy ban Hành chính và An ninh Quốc hội thông qua ngày 5-12 dưới sự chủ trì của các nghị sĩ đối lập. Tuy nhiên, phiên bản ban đầu không bao gồm Tổng thống Yoon.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Tại phiên họp toàn thể, đảng Dân chủ (DP) đối lập đã đệ trình bản sửa đổi, bổ sung tên Tổng thống Yoon vào danh sách yêu cầu bắt giữ.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Cùng ngày, Quốc hội Hàn Quốc thông qua dự luật bổ nhiệm công tố viên đặc biệt để điều tra về cáo buộc nổi loạn đối với Tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol, liên quan đến việc ban bố thiết quân luật.</p><div id=\"InreadPc\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><div id=\"zone-jnvk0c1v\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><div id=\"share-jnvk0cro\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"></div></div></div><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Dự luật được thông qua với 210 phiếu thuận, 63 phiếu chống và 14 phiếu trắng. Nội dung dự luật yêu cầu điều tra Tổng thống Yoon, cựu Bộ trưởng Quốc phòng Kim Yong Hyun, Đại tướng Park An So, cùng các quan chức khác có liên quan đến lệnh thiết quân luật.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Đáng chú ý, các nghị sĩ thuộc đảng cầm quyền Quyền lực Quốc dân (PPP) cũng tham gia bỏ phiếu, dù trước đó đảng này quyết định không đưa ra lập trường ủng hộ hay phản đối dự luật.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Danh sách đối tượng điều tra còn bao gồm Thủ tướng Han Duck Soo, lãnh đạo Phản gián Yeo In Hyung và cựu lãnh đạo đảng PPP Choo Kyung Ho.</p><figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"Photo\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; display: inline-block; flex-direction: column; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: auto; position: relative; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; width: 660px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word; cursor: default; max-width: 100%;\"><div bis_skin_checked=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/han-quoc-bieu-tinh-17338174126671604915237.png\" data-fancybox=\"content\" data-caption=\"Người biểu tình Hàn Quốc kêu gọi phế truất Tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol bên ngoài Quốc hội ở Seoul vào ngày 7 tháng 12 - Ảnh: AFP\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; color: rgb(34, 106, 197); outline: 0px !important;\"><img data-author=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/730/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/han-quoc-bieu-tinh-17338174126671604915237.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 800px, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/480/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/han-quoc-bieu-tinh-17338174126671604915237.png  480w,https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/800/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/han-quoc-bieu-tinh-17338174126671604915237.png 800w,https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/1200/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/han-quoc-bieu-tinh-17338174126671604915237.png 1200w\" id=\"img_790850342361092096\" w=\"845\" h=\"558\" alt=\"Quốc hội Hàn Quốc thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu bắt Tổng thống Yoon - Ảnh 2.\" title=\"Quốc hội Hàn Quốc thông qua nghị quyết yêu cầu bắt Tổng thống Yoon - Ảnh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"790850342361092096\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/471584752817336320/2024/12/10/han-quoc-bieu-tinh-17338174126671604915237.png\" type=\"photo\" width=\"845\" height=\"558\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"lightbox-content\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; width: 660px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast; color: transparent; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; vertical-align: top;\"></a></div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); padding: 8px 0px;\"><p data-placeholder=\"Nhập chú thích ảnh\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(143, 143, 143); margin-bottom: 0px !important; font-size: 16px !important;\">Người biểu tình Hàn Quốc kêu gọi phế truất Tổng thống Yoon Suk Yeol bên ngoài Quốc hội ở Seoul vào ngày 7 tháng 12 - Ảnh: AFP</p></figcaption></figure><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Trong lịch sử Hàn Quốc, chưa từng có tổng thống nào bị bắt khi đương chức. Một trong các lý do là bởi tổng thống được bảo vệ bởi Điều 84 trong Hiến pháp (sửa đổi năm 1987). Theo đó quy định: \"Tổng thống không bị buộc tội hình sự trong thời gian tại nhiệm, ngoại trừ tội nổi loạn hoặc phản quốc\".</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1em 0px;\">Tuy nhiên, ông Yoon đang đối mặt với ít nhất ba cuộc điều tra của ba cơ quan lớn, liên quan lệnh thiết quân luật. Ông bị cáo buộc tội nổi loạn và đã bị cấm xuất cảnh, điều chưa từng xảy ra với một tổng thống tại vị.&nbsp;</p></div></div>', 15, 0, 1, 98);
